&quot;Clerics need to be more desirable in groups because we don't have another option, DUH&quot;<br>
End game. END GAME. Druids here do not buy the argument that druids shouldn't be nearly as desirable as clerics in the end game scenario because they can solo.  To participate in the end game groups/raids every class needs to be nearly as desirable as another, and druids fall short in the END GAME grouping/raids.<br>
<br>
&quot;CH mitigates : DoTs, Snare, Ports, fire and cold DD and debuffs for fire, Disjunction, evacs, invis, levitate, rain spells, ranged AE, and damage shields AND being able to heal as well as the specialist class minus CH?&quot;<br>
