I am not DoTing during the high group/raid end game, I am to watching people die in the futile pursuit of trying to keep people alive with my heals. I do not snare, that is not my job in the high end group/raid end game, and many classes mave this ability. Levitate and invis in the end game group/raid, don't make me laugh. Evacs are superceded by REZ and has been since clerics obtained 90-96%  rezzing. Druid damage shields are not used in the high end group/raid end game. On top of this, druids are a leather class, clerics are a plate class. Clerics get mana regen, as druids do. Clerics get get a ton of the best buffs in the game. Clerics can blast for a decent amount if need be (though not as well as a druid), can get equipment to emulate many druid abilities, have free armor heals. You ignore the dominance clerics have enjoyed in end game grouping/raids and show your envy/ignorance of the druid ability to solo non-end game mobs (downtime, the danger involved, the actual amount of experience gained, the time involved as opposed to the time and safety gained in a group).<br>
<br>
&quot;I dont see you asking for a increase in healing powers across the board&quot;<br>
This is a druid petition, not a cleric petition. Make your own petition/counter-petition.<br>
